<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%=PageTitle%></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jersey+15&family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navBarCss.css">
    <style>
        body {
            overflow-x: hidden;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                transform: translateX(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .content {
            height: 600px;
            background-color: rgba(8, 27, 41, 0.7);
            background-image: url('https://png.pngtree.com/background/20230425/original/pngtree-an-old-classic-car-is-driving-down-an-avenue-at-night-picture-image_2467665.jpg');
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2s forwards;
        }

        .content_alt {
            height: 700px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: #081b29;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .about_logo {
            height: 30%;
            width: 15%;
            position: relative;
            top: 350px;
            left: 110px;
            z-index: 1000;
            background-image: url('https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS2rqo24bn4V6ZQPARAIwg21IEfWZ5Q3SrXbKHKL2awpw&s');
            background-size: cover;
            background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 1);
            /* Orta gri */
            background-blend-mode: multiply;
            animation: fadeLeft 1s ease-out forwards;

        }

        .letter {
            position: relative;
            top: 200px;
            left: 43%;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeLeft 1s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .letter h1 {
            color: #a9a9a9;
            font-size: 40px;
            font-family: "Jersey 15", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .about_icons {
            position: absolute;
            top: 300px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: auto;

        }

        .about_icons a {
            display: inline-flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #a9a9a9;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #a9a9a9;
            text-decoration: none;
            z-index: 1;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: .5s;
            animation: fadeLeft 1s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .about_icons a::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 100%;
            background: #ededed;
            z-index: -1;
            transition: .5s;
        }

        a:hover::before {
            width: 100%;
        }

        a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2);
            color: #081b29;
        }

        .info {
            width: 700px;
            height: 400px;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .info h3 {
            font-family: "Jersey 15", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 35px;
            color: #a9a9a9;
        }

        .info h4 {
            font-family: "Jersey 15", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #a9a9a9;
            animation: fadeLeft 1s ease-out forwards;

        }

        /* Tek tek yazma animasyonu */
        @keyframes typing {
            from {
                width: 0;
            }

            to {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }

        @keyframes blink-caret {

            from,
            to {
                border-color: transparent;
            }

            50% {
                border-color: orange;
            }

        }

        @keyframes fadeLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .altTitle {
            font-family: "Jersey 15", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 25px;
            color: #a9a9a9;
        }
        .navbar{
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="navbar">
        <%- include('../includes/nav-bar');  %>
    </section>
   
    <section class="content">
     
        <div class="letter">
           
            <h1> Oto Expo</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="about_logo">
        </div>
        <div class=""></div>
        <div class="about_icons">
            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-facebook'></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-twitter'></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-linkedin'></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i class='bx bxl-instagram'></i></a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="content_alt">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>İletişim</h2>
            <p>Eğer herhangi bir sorunuz, öneriniz veya geribildiriminiz varsa, lütfen çekinmeden bizimle iletişime geçin. Müşteri hizmetleri ekibimiz size yardımcı olmaktan memnuniyet duyacaktır.</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    <h3>E-posta</h3>
                    <p>info@example.com</p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                    <h3>Telefon</h3>
                    <p>+123 456 7890</p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                    <h3>Adres</h3>
                    <p>123 Sokak, Şehir, Ülke</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <form action="#" method="post" class="contact-form">
                <h3>Bize Ulaşın</h3>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Adınız</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">E-posta Adresiniz</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message">Mesajınız</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit">Gönder</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>